data.text:
A little while back ago, I wrote two articles sharing who my favorite actors and actresses were. Both articles were brief primarily stating why I liked them and what movies they played in.

I thought it would be interesting to go more in depth about how they came to be and create a series. With each article in this series I’m doing, I am looking forward to learning more about my favorite actors and actresses and what inspired them to go into the acting field. Here are the two articles I did for a sneak peak of what will be ahead.

Julia Roberts, an American Actress
